title: (x) Lululemon Logo Font - Trebuchet {Tamas}
content:
Does anybody know the font used in the [Lululemon Athletica](http://web.archive.org/web/20150328042719/http:/ndgstudios.files.wordpress.com/2008/09/lululemon-logo.jpg) logo?

Thanks in advance!
author: Tomufied

comments.content:
Oh. An embarrassingly common font :-#

Thanks.
you know, since im used to seeing it on the web and tiny, i have a new appreciation for those tails on the lowercase a & l - kind of playful
